    <p>{`OpenCRVS has a range of features that respond to common problems that we have observed in civil registration processes around the world. Check these out below and how OpenCRVS responds to these challenges.`}</p>

    <h2 {...{
      "id": "offline--low-connectivity-working"
    }}>{`Offline & low connectivity working`}</h2>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "insight"
    }}>{`Insight`}</h3>
    <p>{`Field agents working in remote locations are unable to complete birth / death notifications as they have no connectivity`}</p>
    <p>{`Oftentimes there is connectivity but it is slow and can disrupt work processes`}</p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "solution"
    }}>{`Solution`}</h3>
    <p>{`OpenCRVS works offline and with low connectivity, and tells users what is going on`}</p>
    <p>{`OpenCRVS allows users to download applications one by one so that the system is not overloaded, and keeps users updated on the progress of the action they have chosen`}</p>
    <img alt="sentReviewPoorConnectivity-2" src={useBaseUrl("assets/system_overview/Key_Features_71621549b7464a72888702cbef3ca122/sentReviewPoorConnectivity-2.png")} />
    <img alt="sentReviewPoorConnectivity-3" src={useBaseUrl("assets/system_overview/Key_Features_71621549b7464a72888702cbef3ca122/sentReviewPoorConnectivity-3.png")} />
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "real-time-deduplication"
    }}>{`Real-time deduplication`}</h2>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "insight-1"
    }}>{`Insight`}</h3>
    <p>{`Registrars have no way of knowing if an application has already been processed and systems often don't have the ability to identify potential or actual duplicate applications or records.`}</p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "solution-1"
    }}>{`Solution`}</h3>
    <p>{`An advanced matching algorithm from is used (Elastic Search) to identify duplicate entries in the system. The system then automatically prompts the Registrar to review possible duplicates before registration.`}</p>
    <img alt="duplicate" src={useBaseUrl("assets/system_overview/Key_Features_71621549b7464a72888702cbef3ca122/duplicate.png")} />
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "usability-of-form"
    }}>{`Usability of form`}</h2>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "insight-2"
    }}>{`Insight`}</h3>
    <p>{`Field agents have difficulty completing long forms in digital format, particularly when scrolling is required and error messages appear in multiple places.`}</p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "solution-2"
    }}>{`Solution`}</h3>
    <p>{`The use of award winning design patterns that have been proven to be user friendly and assist high-quality data entry. Users are presented with one question per page to help them easily guide them through the form and their interaction with the applicant.`}</p>
    <Video url="https://www.loom.com/embed/cfcdbfd21b3d4e38b6bb3b49db98fb81" mdxType="Video"></Video>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "workqueues"
    }}>{`Workqueues`}</h2>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "insight-3"
    }}>{`Insight`}</h3>
    <p>{`Registration staff are faced with piles of birth / death notices for processing and have no way of managing their workload or knowing which applications are higher priority`}</p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "solution-3"
    }}>{`Solution`}</h3>
    <p>{`The work queue is the default view for the registration officer, showing birth / death notices at various statuses, including those ready for review. Higher priority applications are shown first. By expanding an application, full details can be seen.`}</p>
    <p>{`To see all workqueues in the product, check out the `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "user_types/overviewUserTypes"
      }}>{`User types`}</a>{` and see what each user can see and how this helps them manage their workload.`}</p>
    <img alt="Registrar_Home" src={useBaseUrl("assets/system_overview/Key_Features_71621549b7464a72888702cbef3ca122/Registrar_Home.png")} />
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "secure-device-access"
    }}>{`Secure Device Access`}</h2>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "insight-4"
    }}>{`Insight`}</h3>
    <p>{`Digital tools can be stolen and fraudulent birth / death notifications submitted. Also, registration staff can share login details, reducing the traceability of data capture.`}</p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "solution-4"
    }}>{`Solution`}</h3>
    <p>{`A PIN must be entered each time the user accesses the application. Once a week an additional 2-factor authentication is required, including a code being sent via SMS to the field agent.`}</p>
    <img alt="2_factor_authentication" src={useBaseUrl("assets/system_overview/Key_Features_71621549b7464a72888702cbef3ca122/2_factor_authentication.png")} />
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "standards-based-interopability"
    }}>{`Standards-based interopability`}</h2>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "insight-5"
    }}>{`Insight`}</h3>
    <p>{`Systems operate in silos and do not share data. Alternative sources of birth / death notifications and opportunities for external data validation are not leveraged.`}</p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "solution-5"
    }}>{`Solution`}</h3>
    <p>{`OpenCRVS uses a standards-based (HL7) interoperability framework to allow birth / death notifications to be retrieved from service point health applications (e.g. OpenMRS, DHIS2). Standards-based APIs to National ID systems allow real-time validation of National ID of parents and retrieval of personal details for fast form completion.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "data-quality-measures"
    }}>{`Data quality measures`}</h2>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "insight-6"
    }}>{`Insight`}</h3>
    <p>{`Data quality is low because manual data entry is prone to human errors. Records often reflect incorrect information despite supporting documents being provided on submission.`}</p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "solution-6"
    }}>{`Solution`}</h3>
    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Automated validation (e.g. of National ID number) prevents data entry errors`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Client-side validation reduces errors at point of data-entry`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Registration Officers can see the supporting documents alongside the notice of birth / death for simplified manual validation`}</li>
    </ul>
    <img alt="Untitled" src={useBaseUrl("assets/system_overview/Key_Features_71621549b7464a72888702cbef3ca122/Untitled.png")} />
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "digital-signatures"
    }}>{`Digital Signatures`}</h2>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "insight-7"
    }}>{`Insight`}</h3>
    <p>{`There is a severe bottleneck with authorised signatories having to sign large numbers of birth certificates`}</p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "solution-7"
    }}>{`Solution`}</h3>
    <p>{`Digitised certification including the use of digital signatures means that printed certificates can be issued immediately, facilitating a rapid registration and certification process`}</p>
    <img alt="Digital_Signature" src={useBaseUrl("assets/system_overview/Key_Features_71621549b7464a72888702cbef3ca122/Digital_Signature.png")} />
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "performance-management"
    }}>{`Performance Management`}</h2>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "insight-8"
    }}>{`Insight`}</h3>
    <p>{`Those responsible for civil registration do not have an accurate view of service levels and performance.`}</p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "solution-8"
    }}>{`Solution`}</h3>
    <p>{`The OpenCRVS management view provides a suite of service level data, which allow managers at the National / Provincial / District levels to monitor performance and conduct root cause analysis.`}</p>
    <img alt="Performance" src={useBaseUrl("assets/system_overview/Key_Features_71621549b7464a72888702cbef3ca122/Performance.png")} />
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "multi-language-options"
    }}>{`Multi-language options`}</h2>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "insight-9"
    }}>{`Insight`}</h3>
    <p>{`System users are unfamiliar with the default language and as a result, cannot follow the process and make data entry errors.`}</p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "solution-9"
    }}>{`Solution`}</h3>
    <p>{`OpenCRVS supports multiple languages, which can be selected by the user`}</p>
    <img alt="Performance" src={useBaseUrl("assets/system_overview/Key_Features_71621549b7464a72888702cbef3ca122/Change_Language.png")} />
    </MDXLayout>;
}

;
